Data Cleaning & Data Manipulation¶

In [14]:
for i in range(0,matches.shape[0]):
    if matches['team1'][i]=='Deccan Chargers':
        matches['team1'][i]='Sunrisers Hyderabad'
    if matches['team2'][i]=='Deccan Chargers':
        matches['team2'][i]='Sunrisers Hyderabad'
    if matches['toss_winner'][i]=='Deccan Chargers':
        matches['toss_winner'][i]='Sunrisers Hyderabad'
    if matches['winner'][i]=='Deccan Chargers':
        matches['winner'][i]='Sunrisers Hyderabad'
    if (matches['team1'][i]=='Rising Pune Supergiant')|(matches['team1'][i]=='Pune Warriors'):
        matches['team1'][i]='Rising Pune Supergiants'
    if (matches['team2'][i]=='Rising Pune Supergiant')|(matches['team2'][i]=='Pune Warriors'):
        matches['team2'][i]='Rising Pune Supergiants'
    if (matches['toss_winner'][i]=='Rising Pune Supergiant')|(matches['toss_winner'][i]=='Pune Warriors'):
        matches['toss_winner'][i]='Rising Pune Supergiants'
    if (matches['winner'][i]=='Rising Pune Supergiant')|(matches['winner'][i]=='Pune Warriors'):
        matches['winner'][i]='Rising Pune Supergiants'
    if matches['team1'][i]=='Delhi Daredevils':
        matches['team1'][i]='Delhi Capitals'
    if matches['team1'][i]=='Delhi Daredevils':
        matches['team2'][i]='Delhi Capitals'
    if matches['toss_winner'][i]=='Delhi Daredevils':
        matches['toss_winner'][i]='Delhi Capitals'
    if matches['winner'][i]=='Delhi Daredevils':
        matches['winner'][i]='Delhi Capitals'

Best Batsman(In terms of Strike Rate)

In [58]:
strike_rate=deliveries.groupby('batsman').batsman_runs.sum().reset_index()
strike_rate['balls']=deliveries.groupby('batsman').ball.count().reset_index()['ball']
strike_rate['rate']=strike_rate['batsman_runs']/strike_rate['balls']*100
strike_rate=strike_rate[strike_rate['batsman_runs']>=1500].sort_values(by=['rate'],ascending=False).head(10)
plt.figure(figsize=(20,8))
sns.barplot(y='batsman',x='rate',data=strike_rate)
plt.xlabel("Strike Rate")
plt.ylabel("Player")
plt.title("Most Destructive Batsman(Min. 1500 Runs)",fontdict={'fontsize':40})
Out[58]:
Text(0.5, 1.0, 'Most Destructive Batsman(Min. 1500 Runs)')
  • In T20 cricket a player with high strike rate is most valuable. We can see that 'Rishabh Pant' have highest strike rate thus he is most valuable and destructive batsman in IPL followed by 'Virendra Sehwag' and 'AB de Villiers'.

Best Bowlers(In terms of Economy)

In [59]:
economy=deliveries.groupby('bowler').sum()
economy['over']=economy['over']/6
economy['runs']=economy['wide_runs']+economy['noball_runs']+economy['batsman_runs']
economy=economy[economy['over']>=100]
economy['rate']=economy['runs']/economy['over']
economy=economy.sort_values(by='rate',ascending=True).head(10)

plt.figure(figsize=(20,8))
plt.rcParams.update({'font.size':20})
sns.barplot(x=economy['rate'],y=economy.index,edgecolor='black')
plt.xlabel("Economy Rate",size=25)
plt.ylabel("Bowler",size=25)
plt.title("Barplot Showing Top 10 Economical Bowlers",fontdict={'fontsize':50})
Out[59]:
Text(0.5, 1.0, 'Barplot Showing Top 10 Economical Bowlers')
  • Players like 'PD Collingwood', 'WL Mota' & 'RE van der Merwe' are the most economical bowlers who concede very less runs.

Best Bowlers(In Terms of Wickets)

In [60]:
dismissals=['caught','bowled','run out','lbw','caught and bowled','stumped','retired hurt','hit wicket','obstructing the field']
wicket=deliveries[deliveries['dismissal_kind'].isin(dismissals)]
wicket=wicket['bowler'].value_counts().reset_index().head(10)
wicket.columns=['bowler','wickets']

plt.figure(figsize=(20,8))
sns.barplot(x='wickets',y='bowler',data=wicket,edgecolor='black')

plt.ylabel("Bowler",size=25)
plt.title("Barplot Showing Wicket Taking Bowlers",size=35)
Out[60]:
Text(0.5, 1.0, 'Barplot Showing Wicket Taking Bowlers')
  • Bowlers like 'SL Malinga', 'DJ Bravo' and 'A Mishra' are the top 3 bowlers. These bowlers are most destructive.

Final Conclusion:¶

From the above analysis we can conclude that:

  • In IPL most successful teams are 'Mumbai Indians' and 'Chennai Super Kings'.
  • The teams won maximum number of matches when they chose field first.
  • Players like 'Virat Kohli', 'Suresh Raina' and 'Rohit Sharma' are top three run scorer in IPL.
  • In terms of strike rate, players like 'Rishabh Pant', 'Virendra Sehwag' and 'AB de Villiars' are the most striking batsman.
  • 'CH Gayle', 'AB de Villiars' and 'MS Dhoni' are top three players who received maximum number of man of the match.
  • Bowlers like 'Paul Collingwood' and 'WA Mota' are the most economical bowlers.
  • 'SL Malinga', 'DJ Bravo' and 'A Mishra' are leading wicket takers.
  • So companies can endorse teams like 'Mumbai Indians' and 'Chennai Super Kings' for their products.
  • Companies can endorse players like 'Virat Kohli', 'Suresh Raina', 'Rohit Sharma', 'Rishabh Pant', 'Virendra Shewag', 'AB de Villiars','MS Dhoni', 'CH Gayle', 'Paul Collingwood', 'WA Mota', 'SL Malinga', 'DJ Bravo' and 'A Mishra' for their products.
